      "markdown": "56: the people, a people \n\nthe people指人，a peopk指民.The Chinese is apeace-loving people.57.it,one \n\n司比同一物体，one同类不同一.Ilost my pen.Ihave to buyanew one.58. that,this that指代上文所提到的，this导出下文所要说的.E \n\n59. none,nothing, no one \n\nnohe强调有多少，wothing，ho ome强调有没有，wothing指物，no one指人\n\n—How many…/ How much…?-none \n\n\n\nWho指姓名或关系，what指职业或地位.What is your dad? He is a teacher.\n\nbo. anyone,any one \n\nanyoe指人，不接on指可 o ou \n\nbl. who, what \n\n\n\n62.what,which \n\nWhat的选择基础是无限制的，which在一定范围内进行选择.which do you prefer, bananas or apples?\n\n63.other,another \n\nother后接名词复数，another后接名词单数.other students，another stuclent.\n\nb4.not a little, not a bit.not a litke非常，not a bit一点也不.I'm not a bit tired.我一点儿也不累.\n\n65. many,much, a lot of \n\nmany 和可数名词连用，much和不可数名词连用，a lt of可数.\n\n但不用于否定句.I haven't many books.\n\n",
